text: The 2015 Cholet Pays de Loire Dames was the 12th edition of a one-day women's cycle race held in Cholet, France on 22 March 2015. The race has an UCI rating of 1.2. ==Results== ==See also== * 2015 in women's road cycling ==References== Cholet Pays de Loire Dames Cholet Pays de Loire Dames Category:Cholet Pays de Loire Dames
